{"tid":1046020,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李慧詩贏凱林賽再創歷史","createTime":"2019-03-04T02:33:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-19T04:20:31.000Z","uid":25558,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"a1d47468630b8b4b37ef136bd531f76d8449aaf1","tid":1046020,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T02:33:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190304/20625591\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190304%2F20625591&d=i31y%2FnPqUiKwTWzPt1MI4ONdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=c9941e9d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190304%2F20625591&h=821ce023\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190304/20625591</a><br />\n<br />\n李慧詩贏凱林賽再創歷史<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190304/large/a0303a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190304%2Flarge%2Fa0303a.gif&h=78edf25b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n李慧詩勇奪凱林賽冠軍後，興奮得高舉區旗慶祝。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】香港女車神正式登頂！繼爭先賽金牌後，「牛下女車神」李慧詩周日在波蘭普魯斯科夫舉行的世界場地單車錦標賽閉幕戰，在女子凱林賽以不失一局的氣勢下，奪得今屆個人第二金，生涯累積代表冠軍的三件「彩虹戰衣」，創香港車壇歷史。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190304/large/a0303b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190304%2Flarge%2Fa0303b.gif&h=f662f5b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n衝線一刻<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n師妹李海恩負傷完成賽事<br />\n<br />\n今次世錦賽是2020東京奧運計分賽之一，各國精英盡出，為了衝凱林賽金牌，31歲的慧詩放棄上周六的500米計時賽比賽，換來一整天的休息；周日的女子凱林賽吸引27名來自世界各地的車手參賽，香港有慧詩及師妹李海恩出戰，去年亞軍的慧詩氣勢如虹，在首圈分組賽以小組首名直入次圈，海恩雖然在首圈犯規，由原本次名跌入「復活賽」，但她爭氣地以小組首名重獲次圈資格。<br />\n<br />\n在次圈，海恩上演感人場面，她在三圈比賽中的最後一圈，跟對手碰撞失平衡倒地，雖無緣晉級，但她堅持負傷托着單車走完最後一圈未完的路程，精神可嘉，獲全場掌聲。<br />\n<br />\n31歲的李慧詩在次圈雖以小組次名入準決賽，但她強勢以小組首名躋身六人決賽，在六名選手中年紀最大，但仍能力拒年輕對手奪冠，證明年齡不成問題。<br />\n<br />\n慧詩曾於2012年倫敦奧運一鳴驚人，奪得凱林賽銅牌，可惜在2016年里約奧運失利，回港後曾表示未定去向，減少比賽並埋首於2017年完成教大學士課程。直到2018年一月，她才正式宣佈為2020東奧再衝一次。<br />\n<br />\n慧詩現時仍是單車、浸大學業兩邊兼顧，她稱學業有助她減壓，今次是她繼2013年世錦賽的500米計時賽金牌後再奪兩金，個人共擁有三面世錦賽金牌。<br />\n<br />\n■記者徐嘉華  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n港澳台企業憂失外商資格<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\nDSE考生升學 僅兩成願北上"},{"pid":"ccb78c267ecfe30214a072781ab150fd8d946a77","tid":1046020,"uid":212912,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T02:37:22.000Z","msg":"香港運動員 加油！"},{"pid":"4c618bb4b857575f2afad5925dcf255b739c1b8c","tid":1046020,"uid":211461,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T02:57:27.000Z","msg":"佢贏與唔贏我都咁撐佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96348b2cb5cb569d979f67ab006827a28808ac4c","tid":1046020,"uid":78973,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T03:51:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2ggO6NwOMpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D2ggO6NwOMpg&d=i31y%2FnPqUiKwTWzPt1MI4ONdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=dfd70c6c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2ggO6NwOMpg</a><br />\n<br />\n輕鬆羸!加油希望KEEP到"},{"pid":"79e8e60b28ca647131b9542f5f65286a8574a6f2","tid":1046020,"uid":25424,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T03:58:03.000Z","msg":"有競輪唔用用凱林<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n垃圾翻譯"},{"pid":"ccc96bf5f5f33802c94d5239defdac087fd31797","tid":1046020,"uid":37458,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T04:05:51.000Z","msg":"買左樓上岸啦"},{"pid":"07e5297d9f4de951cb04be90feacc9210e247f23","tid":1046020,"uid":107611,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T04:06:29.000Z","msg":"屌，好悶呀，佢成日贏<img 